data.description: Only minutes away from Fort Campbell and conveniently located near I-24 interstate for easy access to Clarksville, Fort Campbell, Oak Grove Casino & Community Center, Hopkinsville & Nashville. Perfect for a starter home or investment property, this home comes with all the amenities you need. Beautiful backyard with nice shade trees along the rear of the property & in the front.  Large open field across from the home provides a nice country feeling.  Oct 2023 Exterior wood pressure washed & freshly painted, Microbial Treatment completed in crawl space.
